OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,FThe mother of a teenage cyclist who
OL,7,Fsuffered life-changing injuries in a
OL,8,Fhit and run crash, days before
OL,9,FChristmas, has made an emotional
OL,10,Fappeal for the driver to come forward.
OL,12,FZach Michaels, then aged 15, had to
OL,13,Fhave his leg amputated after he was
OL,14,Fhit by a speeding car on Bracknell
OL,15,FAvenue, Kirkby, Merseyside, at about
OL,16,F6.25pm on Sunday 22 December 2024.
OL,18,FPolice say the dark silver Honda Civic
OL,19,Fwas travelling at more than 70 mph in
OL,20,Fa 20 zone - with speed bumps - outside
OL,21,FKirkby High School.
