OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,FFighting back tears at the scene of
OL,7,Fthe crash, his mum Maria Michaels
OL,8,Fsaid: "He should be able to get on his
OL,9,Fbike and ride to his mates.
OL,11,F"He can't do that any more. They stole
OL,12,Fthat from Zach."
OL,14,FAppealing directly to anyone who knows
OL,15,Fthe identity of the driver, she added:
OL,16,F"Would you want him behind the wheel
OL,17,Fof a car when your kid's out on his
OL,18,Fbike?
OL,20,F"Would you want your kid to not be
OL,21,Fable to go to their mates?
OL,26,@xD@AOU
