OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,F"It could have been anyone. It just so
OL,7,Fhappened that Zach was crossing the
OL,8,Froad at that moment. He didn't do
OL,9,Fanything wrong."
OL,11,FZach was flown to Alder Hey Children's
OL,12,FHospital by air ambulance.
OL,14,FMaria explained how over the course of
OL,15,Fa week, Zach had seven operations as
OL,16,Fdoctors fought to save his right leg
OL,17,Fbut sections of the bone were
OL,18,Fshattered and missing.
OL,20,FHis mother then had to sign a consent
OL,21,Fform for the amputation.
