OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,F"I had to give someone permission to
OL,7,Fcut my child up. It was over a week
OL,8,Flater when they finally woke him up. I
OL,9,Fhad to tell him it wasn't there any
OL,10,Fmore.
OL,12,F"He begged me for it back. I'm never
OL,13,Fgoing to get over that."
OL,15,FMaria says Zach is as "strong as an
OL,16,Fox" and has healed well but says the
OL,17,Fpsychological recovery will take
OL,18,Flonger.
OL,20,FCCTV and dashcam footage caught the
OL,21,Fcar speeding outside the school.
