OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,FThe car, which displayed a stolen 70
OL,7,Fplate with the registration OV70 OWG,
OL,8,Ffailed to stop after the crash and was
OL,9,Fdriven off in the general direction of
OL,10,FBewley Drive and then towards Valley
OL,11,FRoad.
OL,13,FPolice established that it had been
OL,14,Fstolen during a burglary at a car
OL,15,Fdealership in Wigan, Greater
OL,16,FManchester, two weeks earlier.
OL,18,FOn 18 December, the car was spotted by
OL,19,Fpolice in the town but disappeared
OL,20,Fafter they gave chase.
