OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,FThere were no other sightings until 28
OL,7,FDecember when the vehicle was seen
OL,8,Fagain in Greater Manchester with
OL,9,Fdamage to the windscreen and bonnet.
OL,11,FIts driver fled police and the vehicle
OL,12,Fwas later found burnt out in Billinge.
OL,14,FDetective Sergeant Simon Duffy from
OL,15,FMerseyside Police's Matrix Serious
OL,16,FCollision Investigation Unit said:
OL,17,F"This was a shocking incident which
OL,18,Fhas left a teenage boy with life-
OL,19,Fchanging injuries which continue to
OL,20,Fimpact him to this day.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
