OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,F"It is incomprehensible to think that
OL,7,Fanyone could even consider driving
OL,8,Faway and leaving the boy with such
OL,9,Fcatastrophic injuries.
OL,11,F"We remain committed to tracking that
OL,12,Fperson down and anyone who may have
OL,13,Fassisted following the collision."
OL,15,FPolice say a number of lines of
OL,16,Fenquiry have been carried out to trace
OL,17,Fthe driver and officers are continuing
OL,18,Fto appeal for anyone with information
OL,19,Fto come forward.
