OL,3,CMum's emotional appeal after son's leg
OL,4,Camputated following hit and run
OL,6,FDet Sgt Duffy added: "We believe the
OL,7,Fvehicle was in the Sefton and Kirkby
OL,8,Fareas for at least one week prior to
OL,9,Fthe collision so we would again appeal
OL,10,Ffor anyone who has seen a vehicle like
OL,11,Fthat in the image, to contact us as a
OL,12,Fmatter of urgency.
OL,14,F"I would also ask the local community
OL,15,Fto consider the victim, his family and
OL,16,Fthe risk posed by such a dangerous
OL,17,Fdriver, and if you have any
OL,18,Finformation at all regarding this
OL,19,Fincident, then please work with us to
OL,20,Fhelp identify those responsible for
OL,21,Fthis crime."
